data.description: Step into this delightful 3-bedroom, 1 full-bathroom, 1 half bath home located in the highly sought-after Dellview area of San Antonio, a neighborhood known for its convenience and charm. This property, boasting notable curb appeal, offers a spacious interior designed for entertainment and comfort. The dining area, seamlessly connected to the kitchen and featuring stainless steel appliances, fosters a flow perfect for gatherings. One of the unique features is the full concrete backyard, providing easy outdoor maintenance and a prime spot for al fresco dining. Situated close to a variety of shopping and dining options and with easy access to downtown and other parts of San Antonio, this home offers the perfect blend of suburban tranquility and urban convenience. Come and discover this wonderful home, a true gem in the heart of San Antonio, ready to welcome you to your new life.
